{
  "stem": "232.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We five were in one room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And after a while, later on, this man, whose name was Clement, built a little kitchen in the back, so that we can use it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We couldn't even go through the house to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We have to go outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was a chicken coop.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He made from the chicken coop-- he built us a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The people were very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And his boy was my age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And his daughter was the age of my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we lived a peasant life there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked with the farmers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became slowly spring, and people started working on the fields.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I worked on the fields [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sowing, you say-- putting potatoes in, taking the cows out in the pasture.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went up to the mountains, in the woods to cut trees- prepare trees for the next winter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The trees, when they fell them, they have to dry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They cannot burn in the same year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So trees were felled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I made myself available to all kind of work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for this, they gave me potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us milk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They made butter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was very, very convenient for us, and we could survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the summer, when the fruit came out, this, this, his-- this son of his was-- his name is Jano-- he showed me all the tricks of the trades, like to say how to ride horses.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In the winter, he showed me how to ski, because when it was snowing, we couldn't use the highways.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to get food from one house to another, we were skiing from one house-- like cross country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I learned skiing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
